lead_paragraph: Freddie Freeman homered leading off the 11th inning to give the Atlanta Braves a 5-4 victory over the San Francisco Giants on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Freeman's HR in 11th Inning Lifts Braves Past Giants, 5-4
